Upload Dataset

To view relevant metrics in the Home dashboard, upload the plain_quota Dataset. Required editions: Developer edition and Enterprise, Performance, and Unlimited editions.

Note: When creating a .CSV file, include fields in this order:
StartDate (in yyyy-mm-dd format)
QuotaAmount
OwnerName
Username

Save the file to a location that you can easily remember. In Salesforce, go to the CRM Analytics home page and find the plain_quota dataset. Click Edit and replace data with your uploaded CSV file.

Update the metadata if your fiscal period is different from calendar period. Replace Dataset Data page: Upload JSON file, update field attributes, and rerun recipe to update dashboards.
title: Uploading Dataset in CRM Analytics
